Package: gq
Title: Cartographic Style Management Across Rendering Targets
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Allan", "Irvine", , "al@newgraphenvironment.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3495-2128"))
Description: Extract symbology from QGIS projects, store in a canonical
    JSON registry, and translate to tmap, leaflet, MapLibre GL, and
    ggplot2. One source of truth for map styles across all rendering
    targets.
